The aim of the project is to create an UI for gathering data which will be stored and rendered into diffrient layout templates.
Project consist of 3 parts:
1) Create an interface and MVC architecture to gather and store data, in a form that will be accessible for templates controllers.
2) Create templates that will work with the data
3) Create server side

Current state:
  Polishing (1)

Working demo:
  http://www.pureepic.eu/angular/creator

